2. Data Cleaning

Tasks:

Handle missing values
Remove duplicates
Fix incorrect data types
Detect outliers
Example in Python
import pandas as pd

df = pd.read_csv("dataset.csv")

# Check missing values
print(df.isnull().sum())

# Remove duplicates
df = df.drop_duplicates()

# Fill missing values
df['Age'] = df['Age'].fillna(df['Age'].mean())
